ANACT preventing municipalities from limiting dead-end road length if compliant with
thestatefirecode.
SPONSORS: Sen. Murphy, Dist 16; Sen. Lang, Dist 2; Sen. Innis, Dist 7; Sen. Watters, Dist 4;
Sen. Sullivan, Dist 18; Sen. Perkins Kwoka, Dist 21; Sen. Birdsell, Dist 19; Sen.
McGough,Dist11
COMMITTEE: Commerce
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ANALYSIS
This bill prohibits municipalities from imposing length restrictions on dead-end roads or cul-de-
sacs in subdivision approvals or building permits when the proposed road design complies with
applicablestatefirecoderequirements.
